         <ph props="autonumber">3052.231-70</ph> Precontract costs.</title>
      <conbody>
         <p xtrc="P">As prescribed in (HSAR) 48 CFR <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "
                  base="Section_3031_205_32_T48_7021231112"
                  href="Section_3031_205_32_T48_7021231112.dita#Section_3031_205_32_T48_7021231112">3031.205-32</xref>, insert the following clause:
</p>
                                    <p xtrc="HD1">Precontract Costs (DEC 2003)
</p>
                                    <p xtrc="P">The Contractor shall be entitled to reimbursement for pre-contract costs incurred on or after ___ in an amount not to exceed $___ that, if incurred after this contract had been entered into, would have been reimbursable under this contract.</p>
                                 <p xtrc="HD3">(End of clause) 


</p>
